(48, 1, '2016-06-21 14:24:58', '2016-06-21 08:24:58', '<strong>Attention Parents and Guardians:</strong>\r\n\r\nThe Class Parties for the Gulshan KG and Uttara Junior Sections, will be held on Sunday, June 5th 2016 from 9:00 am to 11:00 am (Playgroup &amp; Nursery) and from 9:00am to 11:30am (KG I &amp; KG II). The Class Party for Class IV Students from Uttara Junior Section will be held immediately after their Final Exam on the 5th of June.\r\n\r\nThere will be no classes held after that date, due to the Holy Month of Ramadan and the annual Summer Vacation. Classes will resume on Tuesday, August 16th 2016, as per the normal schedule.\r\n\r\nThank you.\r\n\r\nBangladesh International Tutorial (B.I.T)', 'CLASS PARTY FOR KG AND JUNIOR SECTIONS', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'class-party-kg-junior-sections', '', '', '2016-06-21 14:38:36', '2016-06-21 08:38:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/?p=48', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(49, 1, '2016-06-21 14:24:58', '2016-06-21 08:24:58', '<strong>Attention Parents and Guardians:</strong>\r\n\r\nThe Class Parties for the Gulshan KG and Uttara Junior Sections, will be held on Sunday, June 5th 2016 from 9:00 am to 11:00 am (Playgroup &amp; Nursery) and from 9:00am to 11:30am (KG I &amp; KG II). The Class Party for Class IV Students from Uttara Junior Section will be held immediately after their Final Exam on the 5th of June.\r\n\r\nThere will be no classes held after that date, due to the Holy Month of Ramadan and the annual Summer Vacation. Classes will resume on Tuesday, August 16th 2016, as per the normal schedule.\r\n\r\nThank you.\r\n\r\nBangladesh International Tutorial (B.I.T)', 'CLASS PARTY FOR KG AND JUNIOR SECTIONS', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '48-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-21 14:24:58', '2016-06-21 08:24:58', '', 48, 'http://localhost/48-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(50, 1, '2016-06-21 15:04:14', '2016-06-21 09:04:14', '<strong>Congratulations to our student KAREEN BAYAZID of Class IX A! She has been invited to attend the Duke of Edinburgh’s Award Ceremony at Buckingham Palace!</strong>\r\n\r\nAlong with our Founder-Principal Ms Lubna Choudhury, Kareen will be awarded by His Royal Highness, Prince Phillip- the Duke of Edinburgh himself!\r\n\r\nThe Award is in recognition of the progress and hard work B.I.T and Kareen have made towards the Gold program- A great honour indeed.\r\n\r\nWe wish you both the best of luck tomorrow!\r\nYou make B.I.T -and our country- so proud!', 'DUKE OF EDINBURGH’S AWARD CEREMONY', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'duke-edinburghs-award-ceremony', '', '', '2016-06-21 15:04:14', '2016-06-21 09:04:14', '', 0, 'http://localhost/?p=50', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(51, 1, '2016-06-21 15:04:14', '2016-06-21 09:04:14', '<strong>Congratulations to our student KAREEN BAYAZID of Class IX A! She has been invited to attend the Duke of Edinburgh’s Award Ceremony at Buckingham Palace!</strong>\r\n\r\nAlong with our Founder-Principal Ms Lubna Choudhury, Kareen will be awarded by His Royal Highness, Prince Phillip- the Duke of Edinburgh himself!\r\n\r\nThe Award is in recognition of the progress and hard work B.I.T and Kareen have made towards the Gold program- A great honour indeed.\r\n\r\nWe wish you both the best of luck tomorrow!\r\nYou make B.I.T -and our country- so proud!', 'DUKE OF EDINBURGH’S AWARD CEREMONY', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '50-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-21 15:04:14', '2016-06-21 09:04:14', '', 50, 'http://localhost/50-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(52, 1, '2016-06-21 15:04:53', '2016-06-21 09:04:53', 'The school will be closed tomorrow (Sunday, 3rd April) for security reasons. We will have makeup classes this Saturday (9th April, 2016). Founder-Principal, B.I.T.', 'ATTENTION PARENTS AND GUARDIANS', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'attention-parents-guardians-2', '', '', '2016-06-21 15:04:53', '2016-06-21 09:04:53', '', 0, 'http://localhost/?p=52', 0, 'post', '', 0),
