(109, 1, '2016-06-27 23:29:36', '2016-06-27 17:29:36', '<h2 class="gdlr-heading-shortcode ">Fees Structure</h2>\r\nThere are six fiscal terms (2 months each). An admission fee is payable at the time of entering school and annual payment is required at the beginning of every academic year. The one-time security deposit is refunded at the time of withdrawal, provided all dues are cleared along with one month’s written notification.', '', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '68-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-27 23:29:36', '2016-06-27 17:29:36', '', 68, 'http://labibacademy.net/68-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
