(120, 1, '2016-06-27 23:56:45', '2016-06-27 17:56:45', 'Tomorrow our institute will be going to organize a ceremony to celebrate this day. So the school will be\r\n\r\nclosed.\r\n\r\nTo have a look at the complete notice, Click <a href="http://labibacademy.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Notice-37.pdf">here</a>.', 'Bangla New Year Holiday', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '118-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-27 23:56:45', '2016-06-27 17:56:45', '', 118, 'http://labibacademy.net/118-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(121, 1, '2016-07-06 12:06:07', '2016-07-06 06:06:07', '<h4>السلام عايكم و رحمه الله و بركته  লাবিব একাডেমির ছাত্র, শিক্ষক এবং সম্মানিত অভিভাবকদের জানানো যাচ্ছে যে, ১লা বৈশাখ-১৪২৩ শুভ নববর্ষ উপলক্ষে ছুটি ১৪ তারিখ ২০১৬ রোজ বৃহস্পতিবার একাডেমির কার্যক্রম বন্ধ থাকবে।</h4>\n<h5>To have a look at the complete notice, Click <a href="http://labibacademy.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Notice-37.pdf">here</a>.</h5>', '', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '118-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-07-06 12:06:07', '2016-07-06 06:06:07', '', 118, 'http://labibacademy.net/118-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(122, 1, '2016-06-28 00:01:19', '2016-06-27 18:01:19', 'Tomorrow the school will be closed because students are going to celebrate this in their own way.\r\n\r\nTo have a look at the complete notice, Click <a href="http://labibacademy.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Notice-37.pdf">here</a>.', 'Bangla New Year Holiday', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '118-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-28 00:01:19', '2016-06-27 18:01:19', '', 118, 'http://labibacademy.net/118-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(126, 1, '2016-06-29 13:47:11', '2016-06-29 07:47:11', '', 'CURRICULAM FINAL', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'curriculam-final', '', '', '2016-06-29 13:47:11', '2016-06-29 07:47:11', '', 60, 'http://labibacademy.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/CURRICULAM-FINAL.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(127, 1, '2016-06-29 14:31:16', '2016-06-29 08:31:16', '<h2 class="gdlr-heading-shortcode " style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #003366;">School Curriculum</span></h2>\r\nAll subjects are taught in accordance with the National Curriculum. Bangla is the medium of instruction.\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We teach here in two curriculum. Students of this institute will be learned at general education as well as Islamic Education like Quran, Hadith and many other Islamic knowledge. They will be able to serve the nation in many ways. So we are proud enough to say that, this institute is a home of Islamic &amp; General Education.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>General Section:</strong></span> This section is like the common section of any other school. According to our Acknowledgement, our government has stopped the PEC examination which has been continued From 2009 to 2015. So we are now trying to prepare our student to do better in JSC Examination in Class 8. Step by step it will increase to SSC level. But we have all the classes as a standard school.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5 style="text-align: center;">Subject for JSC According NCTB</h5>\r\n<table class="style-2 table table-bordered aligncenter" style="height: 204px;" border="0" width="501" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>01. Bangla 1</td>\r\n<td>9. Physical Education</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>02. Bengla 2</td>\r\n<td>10. ICT</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>03. English 1</td>\r\n<td>11. Arts &amp; Crafts</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>04. English 2</td>\r\n<td>12. Work &amp; Life oriented Education</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>05. Mathematics</td>\r\n<td>13. Agricultural Studies (Additional)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>06. Science</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>07. Banglaesh and Global Studies</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>08. Islamic &amp; Moral Studies</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>\r\nArabic Section:</strong></span> This institute is one of different institutes of Bangladesh which offers to learn Islamic knowledge along with the General Education. Student are taught here the Quran and they are able to memorize that fully. Apart this, we have ''Kitab'' division here in which students are taught the higher studies of Islam.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We have a chance for students to attend at Exam Of Hifz Organized by <em>''Befaqul Madarisil Arabia Bangladesh''</em></p>', 'CURRICULUM', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '60-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-29 14:31:16', '2016-06-29 08:31:16', '', 60, 'http://labibacademy.net/60-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
