&amp; Moral Studies</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>\r\nArabic Section:</strong></span> This institute is one of different institutes of Bangladesh which offers to learn Islamic knowledge along with the General Education. Student are taught here the Quran and they are able to memorize that fully. Apart this, we have ''Kitab'' division here in which students are taught the higher studies of Islam.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We have a chance for students to attend at Exam Of Hifz Organized by <em>''Befaqul Madarisil Arabia Bangladesh''</em></p>', 'CURRICULUM', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '60-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-29 22:19:05', '2016-06-29 16:19:05', '', 60, 'http://labibacademy.net/60-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
