(188, 1, '2016-07-12 19:08:18', '2016-07-12 13:08:18', 'It is being announced that the half-yearly exam of Arabic Section will be held on 19<sup>th</sup> may and 7<sup>th</sup> June. The routine of the exam is shown below:\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;">Subject &amp; Pass Mark</h4>\r\n<table class="style-2 table table-bordered aligncenter" style="height: 352px;" width="477">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="215">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Subject</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="text-align: center;" width="215"><strong>Full Marks</strong></td>\r\n<td width="215">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Pass Marks</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="215">Quran / Kaida</td>\r\n<td width="215">100</td>\r\n<td width="215">50</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="215">Tajbid</td>\r\n<td width="215">50</td>\r\n<td width="215">20</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="215">Masnun Dua</td>\r\n<td width="215">25</td>\r\n<td width="215">10</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="215">Masail</td>\r\n<td width="215">25</td>\r\n<td width="215">10</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="215">Total Number</td>\r\n<td width="215">200</td>\r\n<td width="215">90</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;">Routine</h4>\r\n<table class="style-2 table table-bordered aligncenter" style="height: 352px;" width="477">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: center;" rowspan="2" width="160"><strong>Time</strong></td>\r\n<td rowspan="2" width="159">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Division</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="160">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">19-5-2016</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="160">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">7-6-2016</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="160">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Thursday</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="160">Tuesday</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan="3" width="160">From Moring  08.00 to Noon 1.00</td>\r\n<td width="159">Nurani</td>\r\n<td width=