h="159">Nurani</td>\r\n<td width="160">Kaida &amp; Tajbid</td>\r\n<td width="160">Hadis, Dua &amp; Masail</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="159">Nazera</td>\r\n<td width="160">Quran &amp; Tajbid</td>\r\n<td width="160">Hadis, Dua &amp; Masail</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="159">Hifz</td>\r\n<td width="160">Quran &amp; Tajbid</td>\r\n<td width="160">Hadis, Dua &amp; Masail</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Half-yearly exam routine of Arabic Section', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '187-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-12 19:08:48', '2016-07-12 13:08:48', '', 187, 'http://labibacademy.net/187-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
