(272, 1, '2016-07-14 17:52:01', '2016-07-14 11:52:01', 'The guardians of students applicable for PEC examination has been asked to afford the records which are written below:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>2 copy of <strong>Birth Certificate</strong> of the student.</li>\r\n 	<li>4 copy of photos of the student.</li>\r\n 	<li>Copy of National ID of parents- 2 copy of each.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe guardians are requested to handover the stuffs by 16 April 2016.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://labibacademy.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Second.pdf">To have a look at the bangla Notice, Click here.</a>', 'PEC REGISTRATION', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '179-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-14 17:52:01', '2016-07-14 11:52:01', '', 179, 'http://labibacademy.net/179-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(273, 1, '2016-07-14 17:52:37', '2016-07-14 11:52:37', '<span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: ''Tahoma'',''serif'';">The management committee Labib Academy Bangladesh is trying to build it as well-balanced institute but the <span style="color: #212121;">Progress in this regard is not as expected. So the teacher are asked to press their view on the fact that how to develop the academy.</span></span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://labibacademy.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/First.pdf">Click here to see the full notice.</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'RECOMMENDATIONS FOR THE DEVELOPMENT OF THE ACADEMY', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '173-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-14 17:52:37', '2016-07-14 11:52:37', '', 173, 'http://labibacademy.net/173-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
